# User Story

## 1. User Roles

### 1.1 Primary Users

1️⃣ Team Leader
Responsible for:
Creating project boards
Assigning tasks
Monitoring team progress
Managing deadlines and overdue tasks

2️⃣ Team Member
Responsible for:
Creating and managing tasks
Updating task status
Collaborating with the team

### 1.2 Secondary User
3️⃣ Student in College
Uses the application to:
Manage academic assignments
Track deadlines
Collaborate on group projects

