## 3. Must-Have User Stories (Priority 1)

Story #1: User Registration
Priority: Must-Have

Story Points: 5

User Story

As a new user,
I want to create an account,
So that I can access the system.

Acceptance Criteria

- Valid Registration
Given I am on the registration screen
When I enter a valid name, email, and password
Then my account should be created successfully

- Duplicate Email Validation
Given I enter an already registered email
When I submit the form
Then I should see the message: “Email already exists”

- Password Validation
Given I enter a weak password
When I submit the form
Then I should see the message: “Password must be at least 8 characters”

- Session Persistence
Given registration is successful
When I refresh or reopen the application
Then I should remain authenticated

---

Story #2: User Login
Priority: Must-Have
Story Points: 3

User Story

As a registered user,
I want to log in securely,
So that I can manage my tasks and projects.

Acceptance Criteria

- Successful Login
Given I am registered
When I enter correct credentials
Then I should be logged in

- Invalid Credentials Handling
Given I enter incorrect credentials
When I submit
Then I should see the message: “Invalid email or password”

- Session Persistence
Given I am logged in
When I close and reopen the application
Then my session should persist
---
