Story #4: Create Task
Priority: Must-Have

Story Points: 5

User Story

- Access Task Creation Form
Given I am logged in
When I click “Add Task”
Then a task creation form should appear

- Successful Task Creation
Given I enter a valid task title
When I save
Then the task should appear in the “To Do” column

- Empty Title Validation
Given the title field is empty
When I save
Then I should see the message: “Task title is required”

Acceptance Criteria

