---
Story #6: View Current Tasks
Priority: Must-Have
Story Points: 3

User Story

As a team member,
I want to see tasks,
So that I can focus on my responsibilities.

Acceptance Criteria

- View project Tasks
Given I am logged in
When I click on the project card,
Then I should only do tasks that relate to this project,

- No Tasks Case
Given that no tasks are in the project
When I open the page
Then I should see the message: “No tasks found”
