Story #7: Create Project Board
Priority: Must-Have
Story Points: 5

User Story

As a team leader,
I want to create a project board,
So that I can organize team work.
---
Story #8: Send Invitation
Priority: Must-Have
Story Points: 5

User Story

As a team leader,
I want to add a new member to the project,
So that we can work all together as a team.

Acceptance Criteria

- Successful Assignment
Given I am logged in as a Team Leader
When I open the project details, I want to add a user
Then it should appear in the Project details menu

- Sending Invitation
Given I am in the send invitation screen
When I search by email, and click on send 
Then the other member should receive the invitation

- Role-Based Restriction
Given I am not a Team Leader
When I attempt to send an invitation
Then the system should deny the action
---
Story #9: Receive Invitation 
Priority: Must-Have
Story Points: 5

User Story

As a team member,
I want to see sent invitations,
So that I can accept them.

Acceptance Criteria

- Successful Assignment
Given I am logged in as a Team Member
When I open the home screen
Then I should find the invitation icon

- Accepting the Invitation
Given that I am in the invitations screen
When I click on accept
Then I will have access to the project and its data
